Definition:
Abbildung der Datenfelder, die für den Entwurf der Datenspezifikation des Rahmenkonzepts Integrierte Versorgung Diabetes Mellitus Typ 2 erforderlich sind, auf dem des IPS-Modul "Allergies and Intolerances".

Refer to the **[mapping from the logical model of diabetes to the logical model based on the International Patient Summary (IPS)](mappings.html)** in order to get an idea how the IPS relates to diabetes.

Short: Type of the substance/product, allergy or intolerance condition or or a code for absent/unknown allergy.
Definition: Type of the substance/product, allergy or intolerance condition or or a code for absent/unknown allergy.
Who the sensitivity is for

Short: Source of the information about the allergy
Definition: Source of the information about the allergy

Datenmodel das basierend auf den Datenarten für das Versorgungsstufenübergreifende elektronische Leitdokument des Rahmenkonzepts Integrierte Versorgung Diabetes Mellitus Typ 2 erstellt wurde.

Refer to the **[mapping from the logical model of diabetes to the logical model based on the International Patient Summary (IPS)](mappings.html#patient)** in order to get an idea how the IPS can be used in this context.
Administrative Inhalte
